title: Lifetime-Death Clique [2014]
description:
Lifetime-Death Clique (2014) 

Air Date: 12 Apr 2014

Summary: Inspired by true events, a friendship rivalry between three high school girls escalates into a shocking act of violence, and soon one of them is dead. Now the dead girl's mom is determined to find her missing child... and get justice for her daughter.
